{"title":"Unknow","time_limit":1500,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["原创","树链剖分","凸包","数据结构","分治"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6679#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6679","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6679/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6679/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6679"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定一棵 $n$ 个节点的树，每个节点 $i$ 有参数 $k_i,b_i,l_i,r_i$。\r\n\r\n共 $Q$ 次询问：给出 $u,v,x$， 求 $\\max\\{k_ix+b_i \\ |\\ i \\in \\mathrm{path}(u,v)\\ \\mathrm{and}\\ x\\in[l_i,r_i] \\}$（如果是空集则输出 $0$）。\r\n\r\n注：本题加强自[「集训队互测2016」Unknown](http://uoj.ac/problem/191)"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行两个整数 $n,Q$。\r\n\r\n接下来 $n$ 行每行四个整数 $k_i,b_i,l_i,r_i$。\r\n\r\n接下来 $n-1$ 行每行两个整数 $u,v$。\r\n\r\n接下来 $Q$ 行每个三个整数 $u,v,x$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出共 $Q$ 行。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 输入样例\r\n\r\n```\r\n5 5\r\n1 3 1 5\r\n2 0 2 5\r\n1 5 3 5\r\n1 2 4 5\r\n3 5 5 5\r\n1 2\r\n1 3\r\n2 4\r\n2 5\r\n4 5 1\r\n3 5 2\r\n4 2 3\r\n5 3 4\r\n5 4 5\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 输出样例\r\n\r\n```\r\n0\r\n5\r\n6\r\n9\r\n20\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$n,Q \\le 10^5,\\ 1\\le u,v \\le n,\\ 0 \\le k_i,l_i,r_i,x \\le 10^6,\\ 0 \\le b_i \\le 10^{12}, l_i \\le r_i$\r\n\r\n| **子任务** |    **数据范围**    |  **附加限制**  | **分值** |\r\n| :--------: | :----------------: | :------------: | :------: |\r\n|   $1$    |   $n,Q \\le 100$    |       /        |  $13$  |\r\n|   $2$    |  $n,Q \\le 30000$   |       /        |  $24$  |\r\n|   $3$    | $n,Q \\le 100000$ | 保证树是一条链 |  $35$  |\r\n|   $4$    |  $n,Q \\le 100000$  |       /        |  $28$  |\r\n"}]}